---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'May 18, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Refund Policy — SundayRec"
  description="Refund Policy for SundayRec Pro subscriptions"
>
  <header class="bg-[#194280] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <img src="/images/sundayrec_primary_gull-paa-blaa.svg" alt="SundayRec" class="w-10 h-10" />
        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white">SundayRec</span>
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-300 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-gray prose-headings:text-[#194280] prose-a:text-[#194280] max-w-none">

      <p>This Refund Policy applies to purchases of SundayRec Pro subscriptions made through sundayrec.com. Payments are processed by Paddle.com Market Limited ("Paddle"), who acts as the Merchant of Record.</p>

      <h2>1. 14-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
      <p>We offer a full refund within <strong>14 days</strong> of your initial purchase if you are not satisfied with SundayRec Pro. No questions asked.</p>
      <p>To request a refund within the 14-day window, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sundayrec.com">hello@sundayrec.com</a> with your order details. We will process the refund promptly.</p>

      <h2>2. Renewals</h2>
      <p>Annual subscriptions renew automatically. If you do not wish to renew, you must cancel before the renewal date. Refunds are not issued for renewal charges after the payment has been processed, except where required by applicable law.</p>
      <p>You can cancel your subscription at any time through the customer portal link provided in your purchase confirmation email, or by contacting us directly.</p>

      <h2>3. Cancellation</h2>
      <p>Cancelling your subscription stops future billing. You retain access to Pro features until the end of your current billing period. After that, your account reverts to the Free tier — you keep all your recordings and can continue using the core recording features at no cost.</p>

      <h2>4. Free Tier</h2>
      <p>The Free tier of SundayRec is provided at no charge and is not subject to any purchase or refund process.</p>

      <h2>5. Exceptions</h2>
      <p>Refunds may be declined in cases of suspected fraud or abuse of the refund policy.</p>

      <h2>6. How Refunds Are Processed</h2>
      <p>Approved refunds are returned to the original payment method. Processing time depends on your bank or card provider, typically 5–10 business days. Refunds are handled through Paddle's system.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any refund requests or questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sundayrec.com">hello@sundayrec.com</a>. We aim to respond within 1–2 business days.</p>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-[#0f2a54] py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-blue-300">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back to home</a>
      <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
